Hi Erik and all:

Considering that the device access link may be wireless or that the device =
may be operating on batteries, whatever we can do in the infrastructure wou=
ld be welcome.
The Wireless ND SAIL draft allows to propagate a registration up a hierarch=
y of registrars in a mapping system. We could leverage this to implement op=
tion 1 between siblings.
Both drafts will be discussed this morning.

Cheers,

Pascal

